}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== The hub populating this entry is blue. It's S/N is '''UN12220U274994'''.
"UH-07H-R012" is silkscreened on the bottom of the board. :A sticker with "103-12020036" and "1211000515" is also affixed to the board. :A sticker on the case with S/N indicates H/W: V2.0R F/W: A1 The '''SMSC''' hub IC package is marked with "SMSC", "USB2507-ADT", "A1146-AC16", and "8R148739B".
The power adapter included with the device is a '''Touch Electronics Co., Ltd''' M7-10US05R-A (100-240VAC ~ 50/60Hz, 0.5A -> 5VDC 2.0A).
